Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:43.11,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:13.20,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:21.92,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.91,0:23:46.95,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:01.50,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've obtained the Fortune Arcana with your newest bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You are truly magnificent to have acquired so many new powers, one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Only another heart can penetrate into the depths of one's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is Narukami Yu if you multiply it by Margaret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hearts will—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I forgot to multiply myself by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was merely testing your level of understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations. You passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back! I'm the unlucky ninja, Mr. Experiment!{on TV}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You drink coffee, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I got married, I promised her mother that the least I could do was make the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:02:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's become a bit of a habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink up while it's still hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, can you read to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, what book?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I've got work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not make it back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A hit-and-run near Samegawa, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, didn't your wife pass away in a car accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a bandage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a picture of Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from when we went to Samegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy put away all of our pictures of Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He did that right after she died in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about it since Daddy won't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'd get angry if I kept this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask him for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Daddy since he lost Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he feels the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I think so too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too, Big Bro.{HNNNNG}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did God have to create tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? Let's just get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura, I want a melon soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go buy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get me one, I'll let you borrow the notes I copied from Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, couldn't I just borrow them from her in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She has better handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nanako's with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She made plans with Teddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting, Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A bear-y good day to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A bear-y good day to you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana, let's go on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a present if you get the highest test score.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm so jealous of Teddie right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start off with trigonometric identities.{sin^2 + cos^2 = 1. DONE}{8thsin has a trigonometric identity}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The real you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I still don't know who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My memories start with me living in that other world, not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might've been someone special.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But then things started getting weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's when I ran into everyone and asked for their help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I came to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, do you get what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I bet you're a king!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I read in a book that a bad guy cursed the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so he had to wander through the forest alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, that could be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you break the spell soon, Teddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I stumbled upon this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako seems to really like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so could we leave it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you know her better than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Daddy, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Today at school, I got a...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My tummy really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it something you ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The bottom of my tummy feels all prickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? We should call a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait. Hasn't this happened before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it feel like that one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap... I think I put that medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Who's calling now?!{WHY AT A TIME LIKE THIS?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Dojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi? I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A sealed letter? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it from Mr. Ichihara? When did it arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For the love of God— I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,there should be some medicine in the first aid kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Pen-Pen the baby penguin overcame many obstacles to return home.{background?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}He was greeted by a touching reunion with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,my real father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that maybe I'm not Daddy's real daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because bad people are more important to Daddy than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just today he rushed out and left me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They passed it out at school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher told us to give it to our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He said to put down when they could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But Daddy has work,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so he can't go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask him when he gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron! "I don't know" doesn't cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a detective's duty to do whatever it takes to solve a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dojima should be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, Dojima never lets up, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he like that at home too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't convinced the kid's the serial killer, so he's doing his own research.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, he's going nuts over the recent hit-and-run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! Gotta get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the change of clothes you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for a parent-teacher conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They need to know when you could make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fill it out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be coming home tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Nanako doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's feeling better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten since lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the two orders for takeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been meaning to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,about Chisato's accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, I got a call from my old mentor, Mr. Ichihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for his help on a hit-and-run case, and his results just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a white sedan, probably American.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any cars like that around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Records indicate that it wasn't taken in to get scrapped or repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:12:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, there was a similar accident last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The initial investigation we're currently conducting is critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you told Nanako anything about the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisato was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisato was hit on her way to pick up Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a cold day, and there weren't any witnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so no one found her until it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time word reached me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako had been stuck waiting at the preschool all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She was all alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for someone who would never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell Nanako that her mother had been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to catch the criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't have a single clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I {\i1}will{\i0} catch the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should stay with Nanako when she's sick—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:12:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do {\i1}you{\i0} know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, where's that paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Daddy fill it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he said whenever would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! Daddy's going to come?{inb4 he doesn't}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! This is my first parent-teacher conference!{classroom observation, but... that's just stupid}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says their parents are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I framed that picture we found yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens after you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to a place called Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! So Mom went to Heaven, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll be watching over you during your conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'll go to Heaven when I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I see Mom if I went there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a long way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I wanna see Mom, though.{DUN DUN DUN}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an accident around Samegawa about a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you look into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding old newspaper articles on it should be a snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The hit-and-run incident in Inaba.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.66,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim was a woman who lived in town named Dojima Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Nanako's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I vaguely remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:15:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,People in town talked about it a bit at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they catch the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,According to this article, the police are still investigating the case,{according to the article? isn't that shit a year old?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're severely lacking information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll have a hard time solving this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never forgive the creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good ever comes from running! That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncle's a detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so this must be eating at him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookie, Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I put Mom's picture here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, do you remember this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from when we went to Samegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, about coming to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, where's the form?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She means the form I gave you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure "whenever" is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since I'll never make it there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't afford to go when I'm so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You have work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Those bad guys are more important to you than I am, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it! Just forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's gotten into her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako was looking forward to you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That was cruel of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do? I've got work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try paying more attention to Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you actually told her about the hit-and-run...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What hit-and-run?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you never listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}never{\i0} do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, you're stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you call your father stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you care about me, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate me, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't "real."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't my real dad!{;_;}{might be worth rewriting this to be more easily splittable?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll search for her in the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll try Junes. I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't find her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Has she mentioned anything to you lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Like somewhere she'd like to visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...{shorten this line if you can}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'll go to Heaven when I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I see Mom if I went there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's headed for Samegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisato, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,protect Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God you found her.{don't forget to remove this Christian Propaganda or dark_sage will get mad}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you're the family member she trusts the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's more likely to listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still running from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako needs a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When Mom was still with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you, me, and Mom came here to pick flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,just the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... Why did she leave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I want to see Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Daddy, did you forget about Mom?{split?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You hid all of her pictures, and you never talk about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always making you feel so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been lonely since Mom died,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but I bet Daddy has been lonely too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I won't cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to work hard to cover for Mom so Daddy won't get lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good girl, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, let's work hard together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a special day for us as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a special day?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:22:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the day when you, me, and Yu become a family.{you and yu}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What about before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.76,0:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, this is the day we become a real family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... I don't really get it, but isn't that great, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, this cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,From today on, that's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use it. I'm sure it would make Chisato happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treasure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And before I forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Any day is" something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It means "Anytime's okay." I promise I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Families are meant to laugh, cry, and bicker...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.31,0:22:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They spend most of their long lives together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're supposed to be warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:22:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I was avoiding that by chasing someone who had run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who made me realize that, Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it because we're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to continue pursuing the culprit who hit Chisato,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but I won't use that as an excuse to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it because I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, this is my town.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's special to me since it's where you and Nanako live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I am going to continue protecting this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it as both a detective and as a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "beauty pageant"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.17,0:24:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out our group date café...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I look stupid, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you too, Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.85,0:24:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.89,0:24:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll take one.
